msgstr ""

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:94
msgid "DKIM is best-effort: there's no fixed location for a DKIM record the way SPF and DMARC have, so this only checks a handful of common provider selectors. \"Not found\" here does not mean DKIM isn't configured — only that it isn't under one of the names this check happens to try. If you already know your DKIM is set up correctly (your provider's dashboard confirmed it), trust that over this row."
